steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi007b" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi007b" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicol007b" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi007b"
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I create new group API with name "groupapi007b"
Then I should see group api "groupapi007b" displayed in api list
When I select api name "groupapi007b" from list
When I add new API endpoint
When I set endpoint of API to value "/v1/jitera/testing" in floating panel
When I set method of API to value "GET" in floating panel
When I set Name of Model to value "jitera" in floating panel
When I selec dropdown field "Model" of Model to value "jitapi007bs" in floating panel
When I selec dropdown field "Action" of Model to value "Search" in floating panel
When I wait dropdown field "Action" is disabled in floating panel
When I add row Query index "1" with static value - value "OR","jitapi007bs.id","Equal To","static value","1"
When I add row Query index "2" with static value - value "OR","jitapi007bs.jitapicol007b","Start With","static value","jitera"
When I click tab "Request params" in Params of floating panel
When I add row Params index "1" - value "jitapicol007b","String".
When I click tab "Response params" in Params of floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi007bs"
When I add row Params index "6" - value "jitapicol007b","Column Definition","jitapicol007b"
When I close the floating panel
Then I should see method "GET" with endpoint "/v1/jitera/testing" displayed
